							<header class="content">
	<div class="pad fix">
					<p class="entry-comments">
				<a href="http://theumlaut.com/2013/10/28/portrait-of-an-irrational-mind/#comments">
					<span><span class="dsq-postid" rel="721 http://theumlaut.com/?p=721">13</span><i class="pike"></i></span>
